{"thag1.38:0.1":"Theragatha 1.38 ","thag1.38:0.2":"Ekakanipata ","thag1.38:0.3":"Catutthavagga ","thag1.38:0.4":"Gavampatittheragatha ","thag1.38:1.1":"“Yo iddhiya sarabhum atthapesi, ","thag1.38:1.2":"So gavampati asito anejo; ","thag1.38:1.3":"Tam sabbasangatigatam mahamunim, ","thag1.38:1.4":"Deva namassanti bhavassa paragun”ti. ","thag1.38:1.5":"… Gavampatitthero …. "}